{"tid":938913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵癡漢自瀆被擒 哀求「畀次機會」","createTime":"2018-12-12T16:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T18:45:44.000Z","uid":14889,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"77e497df8336dcb5aecb5fb0eb96c5b3bfd6180b","tid":938913,"uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"港鐵人多擠迫，經常出現各類怪客，最新呢位哥哥仔竟公然喺港鐵站對住陌生女性做出猥褻行為？受害人盧小姐挺身而出舉報，癡漢仲苦苦哀求「畀次機會！」<br />\n<br />\n讀者盧小姐周一（10日）約咗朋友喺黃大仙食晚飯，去到閘口嗰陣盧小姐行埋一邊用手機搵緊路，「突然發覺有個人貼住我企，我行過啲，佢又行埋啲」。雖然當時係傍晚6點幾放工時間，但未至於企到人逼人，盧小姐抬頭見到一名男子望住自己，隻手伸入褲襠有所動作，由於癡漢揹住背包，盧小姐擔心佢有攻擊性武器於是走人，「佢追住我，隻手仲喺條褲入面」。<br />\n<br />\n盧小姐向港鐵職員求助，癡漢即時走落月台，職員陪盧小姐去月台捉人，「佢突然彈出黎，自我介紹『我叫陳XX』呀！」兩名港鐵職員將癡漢捉住，對方見衰咗即哀求「畀次機會吖！」警員到場後以公眾地方行為不檢拘捕該名姓陳（37歲）男子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181212/59023364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023364&d=pNmjKUHxl5ctTJihngLYQ54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f38e682c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023364&h=0c62bee2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181212/59023364</a><br />\n<br />\n邊位巴打出左事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8529ae750127c97cbe2884153746463dc20e55bf","tid":938913,"uid":137921,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"佢突然彈出黎，自我介紹『我叫陳XX』呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d0d7371c5127182f2950ff032e1b8f87cdfb2b","tid":938913,"uid":132896,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8529ae750127c97cbe2884153746463dc20e55bf","ti